        </item>
        <item>
            <title>BMW X3 第四代運動型多功能 SUV 登陸香港，售價 49.9 萬起 + 全新運動外形設計</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/01/12/bmw-x3-2/life-tech/auto/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=bmw-x3-2</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/01/12/bmw-x3-2/life-tech/auto/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Sun, 12 Jan 2025 03:00:06 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[汽車科技]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[bmw]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[bmw x3]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1286343</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>自 2003 年問世以來，BMW X3 憑藉其卓越的駕駛體驗，累積銷量突破 370 萬輛，穩固其在市場中的王者地位。經過四代車型的持續進化，BMW 於 2025 年 1 月 10 日正式於香港科學園發表全新第四代 BMW X3 運動型多功能 SUV。此次推出的 BMW X3 20 xDrive 與 BMW X3 20 xDrive M Sport Edition 兩款四驅版本，展示了全新的設計語言，並由美國斯巴頓堡工廠精心製造。</p><p><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1286346" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250110_112534-694x391.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250110_112534-694x391.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250110_112534.jpeg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><h2></h2><h2>動感與現代感兼備，重新設計鬼面罩</h2><p>全新 BMW X3 的外觀設計兼具力量感與動感，展現出非凡的視覺衝擊力。車身長度、寬度與軸距較前代略有增加，而車身高度則稍作降低，從而塑造出更具力量感及運動感的車身線條。車頭的 BMW 雙腎型鬼面罩經過重新設計，細緻的紋理交錯融合，與 LED L 形日間行車燈、側燈及轉向指示燈一同呈現出強烈的霸氣氣息。選配的 BMW Iconic Glow 發光雙腎型鬼面罩及動感迎賓燈進一步強化了車輛外觀的現代感。</p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1286348" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250110_112635-694x391.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250110_112635-694x391.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250110_112635.jpeg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲LED L 形日間行車燈</p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1286363" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250110_114103-694x391.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250110_114103-694x391.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250110_114103.jpeg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲LED L 形日間行車燈</p><p>車頂流線型設計優雅延伸至車尾，清晰鋭利的車身骨線和大膽的側裙造型，令車輛顯得更具動感。車尾則配備了 T 型 LED 尾燈，並由長型車頂擾流板及側面空氣擾流器圍繞，設計細節增強運動感，體現強烈的力量感。隱藏式排氣尾管及突出的輪拱設計，使整體車身更顯動感十足。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1286355" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250110_113154-694x391.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250110_113154-694x391.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250110_113154.jpeg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲全新設計雙腎型鬼面罩</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1286351" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250110_113107-694x391.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250110_113107-694x391.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250110_113107.jpeg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1286353" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250110_113126-694x391.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250110_113126-694x391.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250110_113126.jpeg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲突出輪拱設計</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1286352" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250110_113118-694x391.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250110_113118-694x391.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250110_113118.jpeg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲長型車頂擾流板</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1286354" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250110_113136-694x391.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250110_113136-694x391.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250110_113136.jpeg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲車尾則配備了 T 型 LED 尾燈</p><br /><b>
]]>
            </description>
